reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality for price
reviews.reviewText: Was surprised by these earrings. Needed new silver ones and these are sturdy and look great. Not cheap at all. Most have actual backs not the notch which I find breaks on cheaper earrings.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These earrings are high quality and beautiful! It’s wonderful to have so many to choose from and the price was extremely reasonable!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sensitive ears friendly!
reviews.reviewText: I had to try a few listings before finding earrings that wouldn’t irritate my very sensitive ears. I can’t wear costume jewelry, and even sterling silver will irritate my ears after a few hours. These are EXCELLENT in that I can wear them for days and they don’t bother me at all! You get a nice assortment of sizes for whatever mood you are in, and they actually look like gold. They don’t have that weird unnatural yellow/orange sheen that a lot of fake gold jewelry has. All the clasps and backs included have been sturdy and I’ve had 0 issues. THESE are the ones!! They come in a very basic plastic bag so if you wanted to gift somebody these unfortunately the packaging isn’t cutesy at all. Just something to keep in mind.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute but color is off
reviews.reviewText: Cute! But the color of the 18k gold was a little too orange for my liking. Overall the earrings seemed like great quality but I returned because of the color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these for Christmas for my teen and she loved them!! It came with a huge variety of hoops. Different shapes and sizes. Along with great quality and value for your money! Must buy in gold too!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks Like Real Jewelry
reviews.reviewText: I was super-skeptical when my daughter picked these out. I figured they were just plastic-looking junk that would give her skin a rash and get thrown in the garbage. However, she's been wearing them every day and they do look like real jewelry. Best of all, no irritation.They are very lightweight - I don't know what they are made out of, but they look great and haven't had any noticeable wear and tear yet. I imagine they won't last forever, but everyone is happy with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great value. Bought for teen daughter. These are super trendy but not overly expensive where I would worry about them getting lost. No issues with quality or tarnishing.

There are so many options and sizes. I do wish there was one more larger size. The colour was more pink than expected for rose gold but still love them!
I was quite surprised by the quality of the earrings. They look good on. I have had compliments.
